   <p xml:id="4" begin="00:00:09.569" end="00:00:13.573">YOU MAY REMEMBER THE CASE OF<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="5" begin="00:00:11.504" end="00:00:14.374">MICHAEL SKAKEL, CONVICTED OF<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="6" begin="00:00:13.706" end="00:00:16.042">MURDER, SENTENCE TO DO 20<br/></p>
