   <p xml:id="41" begin="00:01:03.456" end="00:01:07.593">&gt;&gt; YOU DON'T KNOW BUT.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="42" begin="00:01:06.125" end="00:01:08.828">IF THEY SAY NO NEW TRIAL<br/></p>
