   <p xml:id="52" begin="00:01:21.007" end="00:01:25.611">WHETHER TO RETRY THE GUYS<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="53" begin="00:01:24.143" end="00:01:25.945">THAT I FOUND WERE THE REAL<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="54" begin="00:01:25.745" end="00:01:27.113">KILLERS.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="55" begin="00:01:26.078" end="00:01:28.381">&gt;&gt; WHAT I FOUND FASCINATING<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="56" begin="00:01:27.246" end="00:01:30.483">ABOUT YOUR BOOK WAS THAT YOU<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="57" begin="00:01:28.514" end="00:01:31.451">AND YOUR COUSIN, MICHAEL<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="58" begin="00:01:30.616" end="00:01:32.452">SKAKEL WEREN'T EXACTLY<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="59" begin="00:01:31.584" end="00:01:35.154">FRIENDS WHEN THIS WHOLE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="60" begin="00:01:32.585" end="00:01:35.488">THING WENT DOWN; IS THAT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="61" begin="00:01:35.288" end="00:01:38.758">CORRECT?<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="62" begin="00:01:35.621" end="00:01:39.258">&gt;&gt; WE WERE FRIENDS IN THE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="63" begin="00:01:38.891" end="00:01:40.593">EARLY 1980s.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="64" begin="00:01:39.392" end="00:01:41.627">WE WERE VERY CLOSE.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="65" begin="00:01:40.726" end="00:01:43.062">WE BOTH GOT SOBER AT THE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="66" begin="00:01:41.761" end="00:01:44.831">SAME TIME.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="67" begin="00:01:43.196" end="00:01:46.299">BUT, OUR FRIENDSHIP<br/></p>
