   <p xml:id="78" begin="00:02:01.247" end="00:02:05.184">HIS INNOCENCE.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="79" begin="00:02:02.014" end="00:02:07.687">WHY WAS HE ANGRY WITH YOU?<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="80" begin="00:02:05.318" end="00:02:09.789">&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, HE WENT THROUGH<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="81" begin="00:02:07.820" end="00:02:10.756">AS I SPO IN THE BOOK HE WENT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="82" begin="00:02:09.922" end="00:02:11.757">THROUGH -- HE HAD A REALLY<br/></p>
