   <p xml:id="90" begin="00:02:21.200" end="00:02:24.837">TOUGH TIME.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="91" begin="00:02:23.202" end="00:02:28.908">SO, HE HAS, BILL, A VERY<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="92" begin="00:02:24.971" end="00:02:30.776">ACUTE CASE OF POST-TRAUMATIC<br/></p>
