   <p xml:id="111" begin="00:02:55.635" end="00:03:00.373">BECAUSE I ADMIRE YOUR<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="112" begin="00:02:56.969" end="00:03:02.608">LOYALTY TO A MAN WHO WASN'T<br/></p>
