   <p xml:id="114" begin="00:03:02.742" end="00:03:05.177">TIME.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="115" begin="00:03:03.042" end="00:03:06.913">AND SO YOU SAID I'M GOING TO<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="116" begin="00:03:05.311" end="00:03:07.547">PUT ALL THE PERSONAL STUFF<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="117" begin="00:03:07.046" end="00:03:08.414">ASIDE WHERE I DON'T THINK<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="118" begin="00:03:07.680" end="00:03:10.116">MOST PEOPLE WOULD HAVE DONE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="119" begin="00:03:08.548" end="00:03:11.217">THAT AND I'M GOING TO TRY TO<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="120" begin="00:03:10.249" end="00:03:12.585">SEEK JUSTICE AND I BELIEVE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="121" begin="00:03:11.350" end="00:03:12.919">YOU ARE TRYING TO SEEK<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="122" begin="00:03:12.718" end="00:03:13.953">JUSTICE.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="123" begin="00:03:13.052" end="00:03:15.421">NOW, WHETHER YOU ARE RIGHT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="124" begin="00:03:14.086" end="00:03:15.922">OR WRONG, I DON'T KNOW.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="125" begin="00:03:15.555" end="00:03:18.024">I DON'T KNOW.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="126" begin="00:03:16.055" end="00:03:19.258">THAT'S WHY I SHOULD SAY YOU<br/></p>
