   <p xml:id="134" begin="00:03:27.433" end="00:03:30.236">THINK.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="135" begin="00:03:28.134" end="00:03:31.103">&gt;&gt; WELL, YOU KNOW, LOYALTY<br/></p>
