   <p xml:id="137" begin="00:03:31.237" end="00:03:37.410">A LOT OF PEOPLE HAVE ACCUSED<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="138" begin="00:03:36.776" end="00:03:38.644">SKAKEL FAMILY MEMBERS OF<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="139" begin="00:03:37.543" end="00:03:39.845">BEING LOYAL TO THE EXTENT OF<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="140" begin="00:03:38.778" end="00:03:41.447">COVERING UP A MURDER WHICH,<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="141" begin="00:03:39.979" end="00:03:42.682">YOU KNOW, NONE OF THE<br/></p>
