   <p xml:id="143" begin="00:03:42.815" end="00:03:45.151">MORAL BANKRUPTCY TO DO THAT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="144" begin="00:03:44.417" end="00:03:47.019">KIND OF THING.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="145" begin="00:03:45.284" end="00:03:49.388">YOU KNOW, I SAW SOMEBODY<br/></p>
